{
  "id": "RAW_9de34939",
  "title": "Introducing: React Best Practices - Vercel",
  "url": "https://vercel.com/blog/introducing-react-best-practices",
  "date": "2026-01-14 13:00:00",
  "author": "Shu Ding, Andrew Qu",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__9eLiuW__content\">\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-between flex-initial w-full gap-6\">\n    <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">We've encapsulated 10+ years of React and Next.js optimization knowledge into <a href=\"https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-skills/tree/main/skills/react-best-practices\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-skills/tree/main/skills/react-best-practices\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><code>react-best-practices</code></a>, a structured repository optimized for AI agents and LLMs.</p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 max-w-none not-frist:mt-20 not-first:mb-10 mx-0 max-[600px]:max-w-none max-[600px]:px-7 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pr-14 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pl-0 max-[600px]:w-full max-[600px]:mt-12 max-[600px]:mb-6\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"226\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__desktop rounded-md blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__addPadding image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F13SpJ9tCmesIoWp4BrT2fj%2Fc75264f47aec540cde48cd94a19e3587%2Fimage__11_.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F13SpJ9tCmesIoWp4BrT2fj%2Fc75264f47aec540cde48cd94a19e3587%2Fimage__11_.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F13SpJ9tCmesIoWp4BrT2fj%2Fc75264f47aec540cde48cd94a19e3587%2Fimage__11_.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n    <br>\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"1048\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__mobile blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__K44qTG__addPadding image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F14aMyBW08k2S4GJM0NsG25%2Fdfb6035df95d602c85f2b26b048ee228%2Fimage__14_.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F14aMyBW08k2S4GJM0NsG25%2Fdfb6035df95d602c85f2b26b048ee228%2Fimage__14_.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F14aMyBW08k2S4GJM0NsG25%2Fdfb6035df95d602c85f2b26b048ee228%2Fimage__14_.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">React performance work is usually, well, reactive. A release goes out, the app feels slower, and the team starts chasing symptoms. That’s expensive, and it’s easy to optimize the wrong thing.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">We’ve seen the same root causes across production codebases for more than a decade:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Async work that accidentally becomes sequential</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Large client bundles that grow over time</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Components that re-render more than they need to</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">The “why” here is simple: these aren’t micro-optimizations. They show up as waiting time, jank, and repeat costs that hit every user session.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">So, we put together this React best practices framework to make those problems easier to spot and faster to fix.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text-heading-16 lg:text-heading-20 font-semibold relative group w-full pt-6 text-module__fl7lUq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#the-core-idea:-ordering\" id=\"the-core-idea:-ordering\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>The core idea: ordering</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Most performance work fails because it starts too low in the stack.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">If a request waterfall adds 600ms of waiting time, it doesn’t matter how optimized your <code>useMemo</code> calls are. If you ship an extra 300KB of JavaScript on every page, shaving a few microseconds off a loop won’t move the needle.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Performance work also compounds. A small regression you ship today becomes a long-term tax on every session until someone pays down the debt.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">So the framework starts with the two fixes that usually move real-world metrics first:</p>\n   <ol class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__orderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Eliminate waterfalls</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Reduce bundle size</p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Then it moves on to server-side performance, client-side fetching, and re-render optimization.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">It includes 40+ rules across 8 categories, ordered by impact, from CRITICAL (eliminating waterfalls, reducing bundle size) to incremental (advanced patterns). ‌​‌​‍‌‌‍‌​​‍​‍​ ‍‍​‍​‍‌ ​‍‌‍‍‌‌‍​ ‌‍‍​‌‌‌​‌‍‌‌‌ ‍​‌ ‌​‌​‌‌‌‍‌​‌‍‍‌‌ ‌​‌‍ ‌ ​‍​‍​‍​‍ ​​‍​‍‌ ‌ ‌‍‍‌‌‍‌​‌‍‌</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Individual rule files compile into <code>AGENTS.md</code>, a single document that your agents can query when reviewing code or suggesting optimizations. It’s designed to be followed consistently, including by AI agents doing refactors, so teams can apply the same decisions across a large codebase. ​‍‌​‍‌‌‍ ‍‌ ‌​‌‍‌‌‌ ​‍‌‍‌‍‌‍​‌‌‍​ ‌‍‌‌​‍​‍​ ‍‍‌ ‍ ​‍​‍‌ ‌ ‌‍‍‌‌‍‌​‌‍‌ ‌‍‌‌‌ ​ ‌ ​​‌‍​‌‌‍​ ‌‍‌‌​‍​‍​ ‍‍​‍​‍‌‍​‍‌ ‌‌‌‍‍‌‌‍ ​‌ ‌​‌‍‍‌‌‍ ‍​‍​‍‌ ‌​‍ ​​‍​‍‌‍‌‍‌‍‍‌‌‍‌‌‌‍ ​‌‍‌​‌‌‌​‌ ‍‌‌ ​​‌‍‌‌​‍​‍​ ‍‍​‍​‍‌‌​‍‌‍‍‌‌‍​ ‌‍‍​‌‌‌​‌‍‌‌‌ ‍​‌ ‌​​‍​‍‌ ‌‌ ‌</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text-heading-24 md:text-heading-32 font-semibold pt-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:pt-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;:first-child]:pt-0 w-full group relative text-module__fl7lUq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#what-else-is-inside\" id=\"what-else-is-inside\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>What else is inside?</h2>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">The repository covers eight performance categories:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__fl7lUq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Eliminating async waterfalls</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Bundle size optimization</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Server-side performance</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Client-side data fetching</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Re-render optimization</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Rendering performance</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph text-module__fl7lUq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">JavaScript performance</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Each rule includes an impact rating (CRITICAL to LOW) to help prioritize fixes, plus code examples showing what breaks and how to fix it.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">For example, here’s a common pattern that blocks unused code:</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><i>Incorrect (blocks both branches):</i></p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-typescript code-block-module__NOThwW__pre blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__maxHeight\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1d6fc91f-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">async</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">handleRequest</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\">userId</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> skipProcessing</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token builtin\">boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1d6fc91f-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> userData </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">fetchUserData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\">userId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1d6fc91f-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1d6fc91f-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\">skipProcessing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1d6fc91f-L5\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token comment\">// Returns immediately but still waited for userData</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1d6fc91f-L6\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> skipped</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1d6fc91f-L7\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1d6fc91f-L8\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1d6fc91f-L9\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token comment\">// Only this branch uses userData</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1d6fc91f-L10\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">processUserData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\">userData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1d6fc91f-L11\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><i>Correct (only blocks when needed):</i></p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-typescript code-block-module__NOThwW__pre blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__maxHeight\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C298ce468-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">async</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">handleRequest</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C298ce468-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  userId</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C298ce468-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  skipProcessing</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token builtin\">boolean</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C298ce468-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C298ce468-L5\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\">skipProcessing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C298ce468-L6\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> skipped</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C298ce468-L7\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C298ce468-L8\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C298ce468-L9\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> userData </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">await</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">fetchUserData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\">userId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C298ce468-L10\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">processUserData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\">userData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C298ce468-L11\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C298ce468-L12\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Individual rule files compile into <code>AGENTS.md</code>, a single document that agents can query when reviewing code or suggesting optimizations.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text-heading-24 md:text-heading-32 font-semibold pt-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:pt-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;:first-child]:pt-0 w-full group relative text-module__fl7lUq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#how-these-practices-were-collected\" id=\"how-these-practices-were-collected\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>How these practices were collected</h2>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">These aren’t theoretical. They come from real performance work on production codebases.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">A few examples:</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 max-w-none not-frist:mt-20 not-first:mb-10 mx-0 max-[600px]:max-w-none max-[600px]:px-7 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pr-14 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pl-0 max-[600px]:w-full max-[600px]:mt-12 max-[600px]:mb-6\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"498\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mode-dependent-media-module__HJT-FW__addPadding blog-mode-dependent-media-module__HJT-FW__notScreenshot image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5klVTrwVHBbwRXeifeHmAd%2F1b866288fb2c9fb9f22301299348d94a%2FCleanShot_2026-01-14_at_09.28.52_2x.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5klVTrwVHBbwRXeifeHmAd%2F1b866288fb2c9fb9f22301299348d94a%2FCleanShot_2026-01-14_at_09.28.52_2x.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F5klVTrwVHBbwRXeifeHmAd%2F1b866288fb2c9fb9f22301299348d94a%2FCleanShot_2026-01-14_at_09.28.52_2x.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Combining loop iterations</b></p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">A chat page was scanning the same list of messages eight separate times. We combined it into a single pass, which adds up when you have thousands of messages.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Parallelizing awaits</b></p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">An API was waiting for one database call to finish before starting the next, even though they didn’t depend on each other. Running them at the same time cut the total wait in half.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><b>Tuning font fallbacks</b></p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Headlines looked cramped when using the system font before custom fonts loaded. Adjusting the letter-spacing made the fallback look intentional instead of broken.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text-heading-16 lg:text-heading-20 font-semibold relative group w-full pt-6 text-module__fl7lUq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#using-react-best-practices-in-your-coding-agent\" id=\"using-react-best-practices-in-your-coding-agent\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Using <code>react-best-practices</code> in your coding agent</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">These best practices are also packaged up as <a href=\"https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-skills\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-skills\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Agent Skills</a> that install into Opencode, Codex, Claude Code, Cursor, and other coding agents. When your agent spots cascading <code>useEffect</code> calls or heavy client-side imports, it can reference these patterns and suggest fixes.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-bash code-block-module__NOThwW__pre blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__maxHeight\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C16273c8e-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">npx add-skill vercel-labs/agent-skills</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Check out the <a href=\"https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-skills/tree/main/skills/react-best-practices\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-skills/tree/main/skills/react-best-practices\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">react-best-practices</a> repository.</p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel 推出了一个专为 AI 智能体优化的 'React 最佳实践' 仓库，将 10 多年的 React 和 Next.js 优化知识提炼为 40 多个按影响程度排序的规则，系统性地消除性能瓶颈。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel 推出了一个专为 AI 智能体优化的 'React 最佳实践' 仓库，将 10 多年的 React 和 Next.js 优化知识提炼为 40 多个按影响程度排序的规则，系统性地消除性能瓶颈。",
  "summary": "Vercel 发布了 `react-best-practices` 仓库，整合了十多年来 React 和 Next.js 的优化经验。该框架旨在通过结构化的性能调优方法来解决常见且代价高昂的性能问题，如异步工作变为串行、客户端包过大以及过度重新渲染。核心思想是根据实际影响程度优先处理修复，首先解决关键问题，如消除请求瀑布流和减少包大小，然后再处理服务器端、客户端获取和重新渲染优化。该仓库包含八个类别的 40 多个规则，每个规则都有影响评级和代码示例。重要的是，这些实践被打包为各种 AI 编程智能体的 '智能体技能'，使它们能够引用并为常见性能反模式提供修复建议，从而在大型代码库中实现最佳实践的一致应用。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
